  - Apple hanya expose Multipeer Connectivity (BLE + WiFi Peer)

STRATEGI:
  1. Kotlin Multiplatform Mobile (KMM) untuk business logic
     → Domain layer (MeshRouter, CryptoMgr, IdentityMgr) = shared
     → Platform-specific: transport layer (Android vs iOS)
  
  2. iOS transport: Multipeer Connectivity Framework
     → Berbasis BLE + WiFi Ad-Hoc (mirip BLE+WiFi Aware di Android)
     → Range ~70-100m (sedikit lebih pendek dari WiFi Direct)
  
  3. Cross-platform mesh compatibility:
     → Sama protocol JSON layer → iOS dan Android bisa chat satu sama lain
     → Timeline: 6 bulan setelah Android stable
```

